Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.28,0:11:12.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.7\fax0.608231\fscx48.49\fscy96.06\frz-17.0680\frx-0.0001\fry-11.6413\xshad1.85\yshad3.65\org(719.93,1016.83)\pos(707.84,1056.21)\shad3.8\4a&HFF&}‫רוץ! זה השומרים!
